lines.text: [while listening to the Eradicators perform during a school dance]
That band is playing the strangest music. Who hired them?

[watching the high school burn]
And the plumbing was all screwed up!

[on his date]
Tabatha, the 4 major food groups are *not* sugar, salt, fat, and booze.

[to the audience, while rigging the PA system]
They hate it when we do this.
[watching the Eradicators perform at the prom]

[confused]
This doesn't sound like a Zillion Kisses.

[giggling]
Yeah, well, it doesn't look like them either.
Oh my god, she's nuked the school!
We have to stop Dr. Vadar from destroying Rock-n-Roll High School.
